# Assert Never

## Syntactical sugar for assert never

### Example

```py
from an import never

if 0:
    assert never
```

### Installation

#### Linux/macOS

```
python3 -m pip install -U assertnever
```

#### Windows

```
py -3 -m pip install -U assertnever
```
